# my website_parallax_AR-VR

## 📌 Project Overview
This project is a parallax scrolling website based on AR/VR concepts. 
It creates an interactive visual experience by moving background and foreground elements at different speeds.

## 🚀 Features
- Parallax scrolling effect
- Smooth animations
- AR/VR themed design
- Responsive layout

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 📂 Project Structure
- index.html
- style.css
- script.js
- assets/

## ▶️ How to Run
1. Download or clone the repository
2. Open index.html in browser

